stylometry: Some advantages of simulation models are that it allows you to immitate real life situations where you can enter various inputs into a model and see what outputs you get back. This allows you to see which input variables would give you the best results when you have more than one possible input. You would use this in a management situation because when making an important desicion about the company you want the best possible outcome that will help the company the most and using simulation models it allows you to run those multiple possible inputs through your model to see which one is the best desicion and will give you the best results to choose from.
